<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَيُجْعَلُ أَكْثَرُ الفَاضِلِ عِنْدَ رَأْسِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- ثُمَّ يَعْقِدُهَا، وَتُحَلُّ فِي القَبْرِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَسُنَّ لِامْرَأْةٍ وَخُنْثَى خَمْسَةُ أَثْوَابٍ:</span> إِزَارٌ، وَخِمَارٌ، وَقَمِيصٌ، وَلِفَافَتَانِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَلِصَغِيرَةٍ:</span> قَمِيصٌ، وَلِفَافَتَانِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَلِصَبِيٍّ:</span> ثَوْبٌ وَاحِدٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَيُبَاحُ فِي ثَلَاثَةٍ، مَا لَمْ يَرِثْهُ غَيْرُ مُكَلَّفٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَالصَّلَاةُ عَلَيْهِ:</span> فَرْضُ كِفَايَةٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَتَسْقُطُ بِمُكَلَّفٍ، وَلَوْ أُنْثَى أَوْ عَبْدًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَتُسَنُّ جَمَاعَةً.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَشُرُوطُهَا ثَمَانِيَةٌ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> النِّيَّةُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَالتَّكْلِيفُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَاسْتِقْبَالُ القِبْلَةِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَسَتْرُ العَوْرَةِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>